\newlabel{fig:spatial_heavy_epoch}{{3.14}{51}{PSNR vs.\ epoch for QuadCubes with an enlarged spatial encoder (\texttt {xyz}) relative to the three temporal encoders. The smaller spatial-heavy config ($L=23$, $\log _2 T_\text {spatial}=23$, 20.1\,GB) reaches 36.65\,dB at epoch~500. The larger config ($L=24$, $\log _2 T=24$, 24.1\,GB) reaches 37.86\,dB at epoch~500}{figure.caption.37}{}}
